D-Flat Studios, one of Singapore's leading Music Academies is looking for music instructors (Piano, Vocals or Musical Theatre).

Responsibilities are:

  Teach individual and group classes based on programme prescribed by the academy
  Manage students' progress reports, setting goals and obejctives using OKRs
  Developing and inspiring a love for music

Full time and part time positions available

Requirements are:&nbsp;

  Minimum ABRSM Grade 8 Theory and Practical or equivalent
  Diploma or Degree in Music preferred
  3 years teaching experience
  Ability to play-by-ear preferred
